snippet.title: Moonfall - Beta Trailer
snippet.description:
Moonfall has been successfully greenlit on Steam!

http://moonfall-game.com

https://twitter.com/FishcowStudio

https://www.facebook.com/MoonfallGame


Moonfall is a hand-painted side-scrolling 2D action RPG game set in a dark industrial gothic world where the age of Enlightenment never came.
